thread.title: TV | The Walking Dead

author: Fiona Flynn
title: TV | The Walking Dead
text: For those of you that have Fox, you will be lucky enough to get the brand new series of The Walking Dead just 24 hours after it aired in the US. This sixth season has been split into two with the second part not airing until February next year. For now though we pick things up with the group who are starting to realise that if you are among the living in the wake of a zombie apocalypse, you have a responsibility to do more than simply survive...
